													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The mimic falls forward, the lid straining to stay shut, Minsc emerges peeling back the rows of teeth. Standing to his full height, the beloved ranger snaps the jaws of the mimic, its tongue flapping. The creature goes limp and Minsc allows it to thump to the ground."
												}
