												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The mimic practically BOUNCES - then stills, and lets out a short, sharp BURP.\r\n\r\nRakath, satified, snaps his fingers, casting the Produce Flame cantrip, and a candle flame appears over his fingers.\r\n\r\nHe lights the pipe as he delivers his line."
